Package pw.ollie.politics.world.plot

Class PlotDamageSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • pw.ollie.politics.world.plot.PlotDamageSource
  • public class PlotDamageSource
extends Object
    Represents a source of damage to a plot. May represent either an Entity (including Players) or a Block.
